{"tid":2236222,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"柏傲莊I荃灣示範單位吸逾百人 一度混亂 消息指暫僅供VIP進入","createTime":"2020-10-09T10:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:56:02.000Z","uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"647d5ad0249cc05632d68accd8167d9339fb7b87","tid":2236222,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"新世界及港鐵合作旗下位置在沙田車公廟路18號的大圍站上蓋新盤柏傲莊I（柏傲莊第1期）首張價單價錢曝光，1房最平628.9萬起，位於荃灣愉景新城商場3樓的柏傲莊I示範單位，下午4時一度率先開放予VIP人士優先參觀，人數涉逾百人。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，柏傲莊I吸引大批發展商VIP人士到場排隊參觀示範單位，人潮予指定範圍外聚集，據悉多達逾100人。據了解，由於現場除吸引VIP外聚集外，更吸引大批地產代理聚集，有指有人「博懵」帶其他人入場，令當時場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指發展商暫時決定封閉售樓處，除備有VIP證明文件外，其他人不准進場。最新照片所見，售樓處正門位置暫時封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">痴撚線</span>"},{"pid":"41ac13edb8765a6f833f888fd6e6dab3fe0b3600","tid":2236222,"uid":342595,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"『瘋了，瘋了，都已經瘋了。』<br />\n香港好耐未試過咁搶手嘅盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0acbff9af839767ad3a821b8cf62fdb63d1470","tid":2236222,"uid":76469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:22:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q04Vj9qbUY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ04Vj9qbUY4&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=508bc475\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q04Vj9qbUY4</a>"},{"pid":"56f7f362b6984904034800eda4a62145b46cc44b","tid":2236222,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5844cef4dc87a90b36aa30eee874ab3003d6955b","tid":2236222,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5afde639a983c285ebca2360f464